    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>It’s time for the zombies to take revenge.</strong> Take control of the zombie hordes and use your unholy powers to put humanity in its place. Gather DNA research and mutate your zombies, enhancing them with special abilities to help you in your pursuit of world domination. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035320/extras/c8a2a4d4abb7c6e3dcff7f3d9fdf9143.poster.avif?t=1769311351\" width=974 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035320/extras/c8a2a4d4abb7c6e3dcff7f3d9fdf9143.webm?t=1769311351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035320/extras/c8a2a4d4abb7c6e3dcff7f3d9fdf9143.mp4?t=1769311351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Forge your route through the world map, deciding between high-risk rewards or safer paths. Infect and tear through hand-crafted maps, each offering multiple approaches to victory. Use labs and shops to craft your build.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035320/extras/bee1f320d5687f04ed1dddc8948b9ed0.poster.avif?t=1769311351\" width=974 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035320/extras/bee1f320d5687f04ed1dddc8948b9ed0.webm?t=1769311351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035320/extras/bee1f320d5687f04ed1dddc8948b9ed0.mp4?t=1769311351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It doesn’t end when you reach the end of the world map. Humanity will instead come back stronger than ever. Once the world map is complete, humanity's resistance level will rise. Maps have more enemies, obstacles, and defences than ever before. Each stage of resistance will add stacking modifiers to truly test your skills. Can you make it all the way to resistance 5?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035320/extras/3bc227718c4d19bc4d9bd675ea582514.poster.avif?t=1769311351\" width=974 height=424 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035320/extras/3bc227718c4d19bc4d9bd675ea582514.webm?t=1769311351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035320/extras/3bc227718c4d19bc4d9bd675ea582514.mp4?t=1769311351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Craft a unique build. Mix and match unlockable zombies, abilities and blessings to play your own way</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the handcrafted maps as you venture through the dynamic world map</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your zombies in different ways with each new run</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle against increasingly difficult defences with each new map</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather corpses from fallen humans and use them to buy new abilities, zombies, totems or powerful contracts from the shop.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenge yourself through resistance modes.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Early Access</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help build the future of Zombie God as we include community feedback in new updates. We  love to hear the thoughts and feedback of the community as it helps us build a better game. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We are still working on this game, and it is still in Early Access. As such, there may be bugs and other issues, if you find any, let us know, and we will fix them!</p>",
